/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1889 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:82 */
"VDPCONNECT_NETWORK_UNREACHABLE: The local computer is unable to reach the gateway or the remote computer's network while attempting a connection. This could be due to a network routing issue. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_NETWORK_UNREACHABLE: 嘗試連線時，本機電腦無法連線到閘道或遠端電腦的網路。這可能是由於網路路由問題所致。如果問題持續發生，請連絡您的系統管理員。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1897 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:84 */
"VDPCONNECT_HOST_UNREACHABLE: The local computer is unable to reach the gateway or the remote computer while attempting a connection. This could be because the gateway or the remote computer is down or not responding. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_HOST_UNREACHABLE: 嘗試連線時，本機電腦無法連線到閘道或遠端電腦。這可能是因為閘道或遠端電腦已關閉或沒有回應。如果問題持續發生，請連絡您的系統管理員。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1905 */
"VDPCONNECT_HOSTNAME_NOT_RESOLVABLE: The gateway or the remote computer IP address could not be resolvedfor establishing a connection. This could be due to a DNS issue. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_HOSTNAME_NOT_RESOLVABLE: 無法解析用來建立連線的閘道或遠端電腦 IP 位址。這可能是由於 DNS 問題所致。如果問題持續發生，請連絡您的系統管理員。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1912 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:88 */
"VDPCONNECT_CONN_TIMEDOUT: The connection to the gateway or the remote computer could not be established in a reasonable time period. This could be because the gateway or the remote computer is not reachable, not responding, or the protocol service port is blocked by a firewall. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_CONN_TIMEDOUT: 無法在合理期間內建立與閘道或遠端電腦的連線。這可能是因為閘道或遠端電腦無法連線、沒有回應，或通訊協定服務連接埠遭到防火牆封鎖。如果問題持續發生，請連絡您的系統管理員。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1921 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:90 */
"VDPCONNECT_CONN_TERMINATED: The connection to the gateway or the remote computer was terminated by the local host networking software. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_CONN_TERMINATED: 本機主機網路軟體已終止與閘道或遠端電腦的連線。如果問題持續發生，請連絡您的系統管理員。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1927 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:92 */
"VDPCONNECT_CONN_RESET: The connection to the gateway or the remote computer was reset by the remote host. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_CONN_RESET: 遠端主機已重設與閘道或遠端電腦的連線。如果問題持續發生，請連絡您的系統管理員。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1933 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:94 */
"VDPCONNECT_CONN_ACCESS_DENIED: The connection to the gateway or the remote computer was denied access, perhaps by the local host firewall. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_CONN_ACCESS_DENIED: 存取閘道或遠端電腦的連線時遭到拒絕，可能被本機主機防火牆所拒絕。如果問題持續發生，請連絡您的系統管理員。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1939 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:96 */
"VDPCONNECT_CONN_REFUSED: The connection to the gateway or the remote computer was refused. This could be because the protocol service is not running or the protocol service port is blocked by a firewall. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_CONN_REFUSED: 與閘道或遠端電腦的連線遭到拒絕。這可能是因為通訊協定服務不在執行中，或通訊協定服務連接埠遭到防火牆封鎖。如果問題持續發生，請連絡您的系統管理員。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1947 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:98 */
"VDPCONNECT_CONNECT_TLS: The connection to the gateway or the remote computer could not be established because of a TLS error. This could be due to a TLS handshake failure, a certificate check failure or other related errors. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_CONNECT_TLS: 由於 TLS 錯誤，無法建立與閘道或遠端電腦的連線。這可能是由於 TLS 信號交換失敗、憑證檢查失敗或其他相關錯誤所致。如果問題持續發生，請連絡您的系統管理員。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1955 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:100 */
"VDPCONNECT_GATEWAY_ERROR: The connection to the remote computer encountered a gateway error. This could be because the agent is not reachable from the gateway or the protocol service port is blocked by a firewall. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_GATEWAY_ERROR: 與遠端電腦的連線時，發生閘道錯誤。這可能是因為無法從閘道連線到代理程式，或通訊協定服務連接埠遭到防火牆封鎖。如果問題持續發生，請連絡您的系統管理員。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1963 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:102 */
"VDPCONNECT_GATEWAY_TIMEOUT: The connection to the remote computer encountered a gateway timeout. The gateway could not reach the agent or its connection to the agent was refused because the protocol service is not running or the protocol service port is blocked by a firewall. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_GATEWAY_TIMEOUT: 與遠端電腦的連線時，發生閘道逾時。由於通訊協定服務不在執行中，或通訊協定服務連接埠遭到防火牆封鎖，導致閘道無法連線至代理程式，或與代理程式的連線遭到拒絕。如果問題持續發生，請連絡您的系統管理員。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1972 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:104 */
"VDPCONNECT_PEER_UNAVAILABLE: The connection encountered an unavailable peer. This could be because a peer computer, such as a proxy, was unable to handle the connection request. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_PEER_UNAVAILABLE: 連線遇到無法使用對等的問題。這可能是因為對等電腦 (如 Proxy) 無法處理連線要求。如果問題持續發生，請連絡您的系統管理員。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1979 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:106 */
